{"tid":1437854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣落去會點先收到科？","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:10:33.000Z","uid":75514,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d126112cba9e44a05e2717f97f3aad429a7efb27","tid":1437854,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:43:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府跪低</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府對腳比人打斷</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咪收到科囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本我哋就勝利在望<br />\n中國同香港政府而家都只能夠出口術，氹你起大台收兵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即係話佢哋已經冇晒計</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有美帝等緊補刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以繼續堅守冇大台，不篤灰，就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪話核彈都唔割蓆<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">起集中營我都唔割蓆呀</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41e306e37f67d020fa490f395b2a2a9ec3de310","tid":1437854,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27886905300ca3fb6c52e67a555d00f0f0cdcee","tid":1437854,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2